balanceOf(address).notice: Returns the number of NFTs in ``owner``'s account.

ownerOf(uint256).notice: Returns the owner of the NFT specified by `tokenId`.

safeTransferFrom(address,address,uint256.notice: Transfers a specific NFT (`tokenId`) from one account (`from`) to another (`to`). Requirements: - `from`, `to` cannot be zero. - `tokenId` must be owned by `from`. - If the caller is not `from`, it must be have been allowed to move this NFT by either {approve} or {setApprovalForAll}.

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).notice: Transfers a specific NFT (`tokenId`) from one account (`from`) to another (`to`). Requirements: - If the caller is not `from`, it must be approved to move this NFT by either {approve} or {setApprovalForAll}.

userdoc.notice: Required interface of an ERC721 compliant contract.

documentation.text: Required interface of an ERC721 compliant contract.
Returns the number of NFTs in ``owner``'s account.
Returns the owner of the NFT specified by `tokenId`.

Transfers a specific NFT (`tokenId`) from one account (`from`) to
another (`to`).
Requirements:
- `from`, `to` cannot be zero.
- `tokenId` must be owned by `from`.
- If the caller is not `from`, it must be have been allowed to move this
NFT by either {approve} or {setApprovalForAll}.

Transfers a specific NFT (`tokenId`) from one account (`from`) to
another (`to`).
Requirements:
- If the caller is not `from`, it must be approved to move this NFT by
either {approve} or {setApprovalForAll}.
